Hey. I have compiled hyperledger master branch and I am trying to test chain code following this tutorial <https://github.com/hyperledger/fabric/blob/master/docs/API/SandboxSetup.md#vagrant-terminal-1-validating-peer>

When I try to run the validating peer, I get the following error
vagrant@hyperledger-devenv:v0.0.9-f7b0b5c:/opt/gopath/src/github.com/hyperledger/fabric/peer$ ./peer node start --peer-chaincodedev
14:23:52.232 [crypto] main -> INFO 001 Log level recognized 'info', set to INFO
Error: unknown command "node" for "peer"
Run 'peer --help' for usage.

Any idea on how to properly start the validating node ?
